GEL provides custom CSS variants that allow you to apply brand-specific styles using Tailwind's variant syntax. These variants are automatically generated for each brand and work alongside the `data-brand` attribute system.

Syntax: `{brand}:{utility-class}`

```html
<StaticCode language="jsx" code={`
// Apply different background colors per brand
<div className="bg-surface-mono wbc:bg-surface-primary stg:bg-surface-hero">
  Content styled differently for each brand
</div>
`} />
```
